Animals.name: American Bison
Animals.description: The American bison is a large mammal known for its massive size and shaggy coat.

Animals.name: Bald Eagle
Animals.habitat: Forests, near large bodies of open water
Animals.description: The bald eagle is a bird of prey found in North America, recognized by its white head and tail.

Animals.name: Eastern Box Turtle
Animals.description: The Eastern box turtle is a terrestrial turtle known for its domed shell and ability to retract into it.

Animals.name: American Bullfrog
Animals.description: The American bullfrog is a large frog known for its deep croak and voracious appetite.

Animals.name: Rainbow Trout
Animals.description: The rainbow trout is a species of salmonid fish known for its vibrant coloration and adaptability.

Animals.name: Monarch Butterfly
Animals.description: The monarch butterfly is known for its long migrations and distinctive orange and black wings.

Animals.name: Black Widow Spider
Animals.description: The black widow spider is known for its glossy black body and red hourglass marking.

Animals.name: Opossum
Animals.description: The opossum is the only marsupial native to North America, known for its ability to play dead when threatened.

Sightings.notes: Saw this magnificent bison in my backyard!
He was actually very nice, he lives with me now.
